 "18188321977368293", "text": "Does it mean you’ve become an expert at spinning around the planet?", "timestamp": 1774764207}, {"author": "24richfx", "author_id": "44618126669", "id": "17918067438322733", "text": "Happy AEON'th birthday MY FRIEND ❤️🙌", "timestamp": 1774744715}, {"author": "danae_under_the_stars", "author_id": "6775603918", "id": "18118081621649317", "text": "I promise", "timestamp": 1774741133}, {"author": "melonikainalo69", "author_id": "8076879656", "id": "18099252622972034", "text": "Oletko koskaan yksin?", "timestamp": 1774731546}, {"author": "tanya_awasthy", "author_id": "2977344349", "id": "18078537800390901", "text": "Happy birthday sir 🥳", "timestamp": 1774725484}, {"author": "jasonsiu8", "author_id": "64542947995", "id": "18089763475935906", "text": "Happy birthday👏", "timestamp": 1774718009}], "thumbnails": [{"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/657183960_1276753427121008_6462274937856548889_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5leHBlcmltZW50YWwifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFHPCQeoo1--nUDvPDVlUlxinIDEF5e8Xcyz1wQo1uSAVmaKMDK6d1hYU0sMtENexA&_nc_ohc=9RhmBzph4hoQ7kNvwFvXY6m&_nc_gid=6JodsTpx1OlwyODK1ZYhHw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0nzYJSf2WGNr8PTlC4BE9wt0PoYyVVwIEu6Qb8DPNSyw&oe=69D7973C&_nc_sid=d885a2", "width": 640, "height": 1136, "id": "0", "resolution": "640x1136"}, {"url": "https://scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com/v/t51.71878-15/657183960_1276753427121008_6462274937856548889_n.jpg?stp=dst-jpg_e15_tt6&efg=eyJ2ZW5jb2RlX3RhZyI6ImltYWdlX3VybGdlbi42NDB4MTEzNi5zZHIuZjcxODc4Lm5mcmFtZV9jb3Zlcl9mcmFtZS5leHBlcmltZW50YWwifQ&_nc_ht=scontent-yyz1-1.cdninstagram.com&_nc_cat=108&_nc_oc=Q6cZ2gFHPCQeoo1--nUDvPDVlUlxinIDEF5e8Xcyz1wQo1uSAVmaKMDK6d1hYU0sMtENexA&_nc_ohc=9RhmBzph4hoQ7kNvwFvXY6m&_nc_gid=6JodsTpx1OlwyODK1ZYhHw&edm=ANTKIIoBAAAA&ccb=7-5&oh=00_Af0nzYJSf2WGNr8PTlC4BE9wt0PoYyVVwIEu6Qb8DPNSyw&oe=69D